New Records: Australia's Adam Zampa was named Player of the Match
Key Match Events: England's top order went, making it tough for the middle order
Adam Zampa bowled well, making it difficult for England to hit him
Post-Match Reflections: Australia captain Mitchell Marsh relished the team's performance
England captain Jos Buttler reflected on the defeat, saying Australia played well and put them under pressure
Adam Zampa said Australia's bowling attack has great depth and they all play different roles
Miscellaneous Highlights: Australia went to the top of the table
England must win their final games against Namibia and Oman to have a chance of qualification into the Super Eights
The match was played in the ICC T20 World Cup 2024 in Barbados
